class.name: meta.class.actionscript.3
class.begin:
(?x)							# Turn on extended mode
					  ^\s*							# Start of line and optional whitespace
					  (\b(dynamic|final)\b\s+)?		# Optional dynamic or final
					  (\b(internal|public)\b\s+)?	# Optional public or internal
					  (\b(dynamic|final)\b\s+)?		# Optional dynamic or final
					  (?=class)						# Class definition

class-name.begin:
(?x)
					 (?<=class)		# look behind for class
					 \s+			# At least one character of whitespace
			  		 (\w+)\b		# The name of the class.

interface.name: meta.interface.actionscript.3
interface.begin:
(?x)				# Turn on extended mode
					 ^					# a line beginning with
					 \s*				# some optional space
					 (\b(public)\b\s+)	# namespace
					 (interface)\s+		# interface declaration and at least one char. of whitespace
					 (\w+)              # interface name.
					 \s*

patterns.name: meta.definition.getter.interface.actionscript.3
patterns.begin:
(?x)
							 ^\s*                   # start of line, optional whitespace
							 (function)\s+          # function declaration
							 (\bget\b)\s+           # accessor
							 (\w+)                  # Method name.
							 \s*
							 (\()
							 \s*
							 (.*)?
							 \s*
							 (\))
							 \s*:\s*

patterns.name: meta.definition.setter.interface.actionscript.3
patterns.begin:
(?x)
							 ^\s*                   # start of line, optional whitespace
							 (function)\s+          # function declaration
							 (\bset\b)\s+           # accessor
							 (\w+)                  # method name
							 \s*
							 (\()

interface-methods.name: meta.definition.method.interface.actionscript.3
interface-methods.begin:
(?x)
					 ^\s*                   # start of line, optional whitespace
					 (function)\s+          # function declaration
					 (\s*\w+)               # Method name.
					 \s*(\()

method.name: meta.definition.method.actionscript.3
method.begin:
(?x)
			         ^\s*
    			     ((override|static)\s+){0,2}                                  # Optional override or static
    			     (public|private|protected|internal|final|dynamic|\w+)\s+ # Namespace
    			     ((override|static)\s+){0,2}                                           # Optional static.
    			     (function)\s+
    			     (\s*\w+)                                                 # Method name.
    			     \s*(\()

patterns.name: meta.definition.setter.actionscript.3
patterns.begin:
(?x)                                                               # Extended mode
					         ^\s*                                                               # Start of line, optional whitespace
    			             ((override|static)\s+){0,2}                                            # Optional override
    			             (public|private|protected|internal|final|dynamic|\w+)\s+           # namespace declaration
    			             ((static)\s+){0,2}                                                     # Optional static
    			             (function)\s*                                                      # function declaration
                             (set)\s+                                                           # set declaration
                             (\w+)\s*                                                           # getter name, optional whitespace
    			             (\()

method-parameters.match:
(?x)
					 (\$?\w+)       # paramater name
					 \s*(\:)\s*     # type seperator
					 (
						(\w+)
						|
						(\*)        # followed by class or wildcard
					 )
					 |(\.\.\.)      # or rest...
